    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～～ん！\nお疲れ様です、お待ちしてました！",
      "startTime": 8.9229286512,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 199.9999999999993,
          "startTime": 7.4141270638
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、わざわざ待っててくれたのか\n観光大使の仕事もあるのに、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　{user}さんが山形に\n来てくれて、凄く嬉しいです。待ち伏せ作戦成功です！",
      "startTime": 21.3235148431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんは入れ違いで\n今朝別の仕事があるので東京に戻りました",
      "startTime": 29.9591354294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも\n今日はここにお泊りするんですよね？",
      "startTime": 35.1568481764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、山形にいる間はここに滞在する予定だよ\nすみれ達は、昨日泊まったんだよな。どうだった？",
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ここ、すっごくいいお宿ですよ\n温泉も気持ちいいですし、お鍋も美味しかったな～",
      "startTime": 50.7246256194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "地元の素材を使った山菜鍋なんて\n東京だとなかなか食べられないですから",
      "startTime": 58.8246256194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、三人でのんびり温泉にも入れましたよ\nトリエルの大事な思い出がまた一つ増えました！",
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげですね！\n旅館とお鍋を予約してくれて、ありがとうございました",
      "startTime": 73.3246266367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "喜んでもらえて俺も嬉しいよ\nトリエルの打ち上げっていったら鍋だと思ってな",
      "startTime": 80.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりそうですよね！\n私達も同じことを言いながらお鍋をつつきました",
      "startTime": 85.9969619753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯の後は温泉に入って、温泉の後は……\nふふっ、浴衣で卓球したんです",
      "startTime": 95.3302953086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "運動関係は、私達三人の中だと\n瑠依ちゃんが最強……だと思うじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 102.2302953086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依は運動神経がいいからなぁ\nん？　もしかして違ったのか？",
      "startTime": 110.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "なんと！　温泉ピンポン最強は、優ちゃんでした！",
      "startTime": 113.0995695117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "表情が変わらないし、どこに打ち込むか分からなくて\n瑠依ちゃんがフェイントに引っかかって……",
      "startTime": 122.7329030993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "気付いたら優ちゃんが勝っていたんです\n瑠依ちゃんも悔しそうだけど楽しそうでした",
      "startTime": 129.1329030993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "本当に楽しかった～……\nおかげで、今日からまた、元気一杯頑張れます！",
      "startTime": 135.8662364326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "充実したオフを過ごせたみたいで良かったよ\nそういえば、今日からはどこに泊まるんだ？",
      "startTime": 142.9511227813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、実家が近いので\nしばらくは実家からお仕事に向かいます",
      "startTime": 148.1135830564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "チェックアウトは済んでるんですけど\n{user}さんをお迎えしたくて待ってたんです",
      "startTime": 153.4469163897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "今の私は『山形の顔』ですから！\nどうですか？　元気の出る顔でしょう？",
      "startTime": 160.6135830564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、すみれの顔を見れて凄く元気がもらえたよ\nさすが、山形の観光大使に指名されるだけのことはある",
      "startTime": 168.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、お仕事のために山形のことを調べ直してみて\n改めて山形っていい所だなぁって思いました",
      "startTime": 178.0146038058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "私、地元が大好きなので、やる気がみなぎってます！\n沢山紹介したい所があるんですよ～！",
      "startTime": 187.6812704725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、優が凄く羨ましがっていたぞ",
      "startTime": 190.6812717441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いつか絶対京都の観光大使をやるんだ、って\n優秘蔵の京都観光スポットメモを見せられたよ",
      "startTime": 198.1666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
